{"tid":2098414,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"加熱煙，電子煙 關注","createTime":"2020-07-07T12:54:07.000Z","updateTime":"2020-07-09T03:51:06.000Z","uid":191019,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"150fe6f21182de3efab9d4003d07391d7bb8006c","tid":2098414,"uid":191019,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-07T12:54:07.000Z","msg":"之前都有人提過其實究竟點解冇乜人提香港啲電子煙，加煙油個種，啲油係冇尼古丁架。<br />\n小弟做煙民都差啲中過招<br />\n<br />\n首先都要提一提各位煙巴 <br />\n現時吸食電子煙與成煙一樣並無觸犯法例，但在禁煙區吸食電子煙，定額罰款為1,500港元，或經定罪後可判罰款5,000港元。 <br />\n政府現建議禁止將電子煙進口至香港，在外地購買電子煙回港會犯法，最高可罰款5萬元<br />\n下面係關注組既page 有心理解下既巴絲可以去睇睇<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/187849085098075/posts/675009986381980/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2F187849085098075%2Fposts%2F675009986381980%2F&d=mNwaOXjJ1pf0GC%2FIettivfGl%2B26pDsgLotMYn9d4AWI%3D&h=fa46d438\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/187849085098075/posts/675009986381980/</a>"},{"pid":"dce2ba4578f72e060a5681972a3c7214c2c87d31","tid":2098414,"uid":191019,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-07T13:08:25.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/e9DRz5L.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fe9DRz5L.jpg&h=35641d5f&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"bde5a3309669648436ca6712ecc6806e741c4310","tid":2098414,"uid":127770,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-07T14:09:31.000Z","msg":"啱呀，禁埋咖啡奶茶<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8e19326b7d46a708bd2e783b762549082b05f77d","tid":2098414,"uid":209337,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-08T03:48:57.000Z","msg":"禁禁禁，咩都禁！無人理過我地咁"},{"pid":"404b66fafa16aac44bc889bffeb99da774825b7c","tid":2098414,"uid":209337,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-08T03:49:12.000Z","msg":"要戒煙一早戒咗啦"},{"pid":"903d4aa9dd52ddcd1a797e2e373d5c3d24168